00:11:29.105 --> 00:11:29.898 position:50% align:center
[MEGANE]
Ah!

00:11:29.981 --> 00:11:31.441 position:50% align:center
[POCHA grunts]

00:11:31.524 --> 00:11:36.905 position:50% align:center
[CAP] What was that about being
on Rin's team, you traitor?

00:11:36.988 --> 00:11:38.448 position:50% align:center
