to witness it.

00:12:25.245 --> 00:12:28.707 position:50% align:center
Yes! Down she goes!
Serves her right!

00:12:28.790 --> 00:12:30.709 position:50% align:center
You're merciless.

00:12:30.792 --> 00:12:32.919 position:50% align:center
