naive bubble, little fish,

00:12:33.003 --> 00:12:35.672 position:50% align:center
but everyone's
like this nowadays.

00:12:41.177 --> 00:12:43.638 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI]
What's wrong?

00:12:43.722 --> 00:12:47.350 position:50% align:center
[YUKI]
Nothing. Nothing at all.

00:13:01.698 --> 00:13:03.199 position:50% align:center
[MIMI]
Preparations complete.

00:13:03.283 --> 00:13:06.327 position:50% align:center
