Depends on the battery girl.

00:13:14.377 --> 00:13:17.005 position:50% align:center
Whatever physical form
her passion takes.

00:13:17.088 --> 00:13:17.881 position:50% align:center
Ah.

00:13:17.964 --> 00:13:23.970 position:50% align:center
[YUKI humming]

00:13:27.015 --> 00:13:30.226 position:50% align:center
