This is my battle uniform.

00:14:55.812 --> 00:15:00.817 position:50% align:center
[siren wails]

00:15:02.986 --> 00:15:04.446 position:50% align:center
[OPERATOR A]
Signal detected!

00:15:04.529 --> 00:15:07.574 position:50% align:center
An enemy has broken through
the Kanda River defense line!

00:15:07.657 --> 00:15:10.410 position:50% align:center
