flying Garann?

00:15:10.493 --> 00:15:13.246 position:50% align:center
Guess someone got an upgrade.

00:15:13.329 --> 00:15:15.040 position:50% align:center
[YAKUMO]
How do you find the new model?

00:15:15.123 --> 00:15:18.126 position:50% align:center
Well, I wish I could say
that it handled better.

00:15:18.209 --> 00:15:20.128 position:50% align:center
I like a challenge, though.

00:15:20.211 --> 00:15:21.379 position:50% align:center
[YAKUMO]
In that case,

00:15:21.463 --> 00:15:23.882 position:50% align:center
come back so we can make
the final adjustments.

00:15:23.965 --> 00:15:26.926 position:50% align:center
[AKATSUKI] The test is
over. Return to base.

00:15:27.010 --> 00:15:30.347 position:50% align:center
Of course. I hear you
loud 'n' clear, sir.

00:15:30.430 --> 00:15:32.974 position:50% align:center
But order refused!

00:15:33.058 --> 00:15:35.685 position:50% align:center
[OPERATOR A] Enemy Garann is
closing in on our shores!

00:15:35.769 --> 00:15:38.438 position:50% align:center
[BALZAC]
What's Rin's status?

00:15:38.521 --> 00:15:42.484 position:50% align:center
Za-ba-ba-burn! Za-ba-ba-burn.

00:15:46.529 --> 00:15:47.739 position:50% align:center
[BALZAC]
Sorry to spring this on you,

00:15:47.822 --> 00:15:49.449 position:50% align:center
but you're our only hope.

00:15:49.532 --> 00:15:51.534 position:50% align:center
[YUKI] No worries!
Leave it to me, Commander!

00:15:51.618 --> 00:15:53.828 position:50% align:center
I guess this is what you
call a guerrilla gig!

00:15:53.912 --> 00:15:55.413 position:50% align:center
It'll be the perfect debut!

00:15:55.497 --> 00:15:57.374 position:50% align:center
Especially for a
little battery girl!

00:15:57.457 --> 00:16:01.002 position:50% align:center
[RESISTANCE]
Yuki-rin!

00:16:01.086 --> 00:16:03.880 position:50% align:center
You can do it, Yuki-rin!

00:16:03.963 --> 00:16:06.174 position:50% align:center
[YUKI] This makes me
so hoppy, you guys!

00:16:06.257 --> 00:16:08.093 position:50% align:center
Like, it's not even bunny!

00:16:08.176 --> 00:16:08.968 position:50% align:center
[RESISTENCE cheers]

00:16:09.052 --> 00:16:10.595 position:50% align:center
[giggles]

00:16:10.679 --> 00:16:13.098 position:50% align:center
From now on, I won't just be
a girl from Rabbit Foot.

00:16:13.181 --> 00:16:16.476 position:50% align:center
I'll be the bun-ifide idol of
freedom for the resistance!

00:16:16.559 --> 00:16:18.436 position:50% align:center
Here I go!

00:16:18.520 --> 00:16:22.315 position:50% align:center
[RESISTENCE cheers]

00:16:22.399 --> 00:16:23.775 position:50% align:center
[MIMI]
Listen up, Hosomichi.

00:16:23.858 --> 00:16:27.070 position:50% align:center
Unlike Rin, Yuki's never
operated a Garanndoll before.

00:16:27.153 --> 00:16:28.863 position:50% align:center
