keep her energized.

00:16:28.947 --> 00:16:32.158 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I know. I'll keep
it under control.

00:16:34.119 --> 00:16:37.122 position:50% align:center
[RESISTANCE]
Yuki-rin! Yuki-rin! Yuki-rin...!

00:16:37.205 --> 00:16:40.208 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI]
Huh? Huh?

00:16:40.291 --> 00:16:41.543 position:50% align:center
Huh?!

00:16:41.626 --> 00:16:43.586 position:50% align:center
