honest, do I look cute?

00:16:48.550 --> 00:16:49.884 position:50% align:center
What? Who cares?

00:16:49.968 --> 00:16:54.681 position:50% align:center
Just answer, you idiot! Well?

00:16:54.764 --> 00:16:58.101 position:50% align:center
Random, I know, but do you
think I can become an idol?

00:16:58.184 --> 00:17:01.938 position:50% align:center
The type that people
can't help but love?

00:17:02.939 --> 00:17:04.899 position:50% align:center
I definitely see
that happening!

00:17:04.983 --> 00:17:06.693 position:50% align:center
If you mix all your
talents together,

00:17:06.776 --> 00:17:09.320 position:50% align:center
you're, like, the perfect
idol everybody wants!

00:17:09.404 --> 00:17:11.990 position:50% align:center
That everybody wants?

00:17:14.451 --> 00:17:20.290 position:50% align:center
Ah, okay. Yeah.
Ready to bounce when you are!

00:17:28.548 --> 00:17:31.718 position:50% align:center
