Shout, my dear boy!

00:17:34.804 --> 00:17:36.514 position:50% align:center
The sound of your voice
will supply her

00:17:36.598 --> 00:17:38.933 position:50% align:center
with all the strength she needs!

00:17:39.017 --> 00:17:43.813 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI]
Seriously? Fine! Whatever!

00:17:43.897 --> 00:17:47.108 position:50% align:center
Rabbit! Foot! Love! Whoo!

00:17:47.192 --> 00:17:50.403 position:50% align:center
[FANS]
Rabbit! Foot! Love! Whoo!

00:17:50.487 --> 00:17:56.493 position:50% align:center
Rabbit! Foot! Love! Whoo!
Rabbit! Foot! Love! Whoo...!

