wallowing in now?

00:18:29.651 --> 00:18:31.986 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI]
Yuki-rin!

00:18:39.994 --> 00:18:42.247 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI]
Go and take the stage!

00:18:42.330 --> 00:18:47.794 position:50% align:center
[FANS]
Rabbit! Foot! Love! Whoo!

00:18:49.295 --> 00:18:50.714 position:50% align:center
What?

00:18:52.841 --> 00:18:54.175 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI grunts]

00:18:57.262 --> 00:18:58.888 position:50% align:center
[giggles]

00:18:58.972 --> 00:19:02.934 position:50% align:center
