you all waiting!

00:19:05.395 --> 00:19:07.105 position:50% align:center
[YUKI]
Tee-hee!

00:19:08.982 --> 00:19:10.859 position:50% align:center
Hey, guys!

00:19:10.942 --> 00:19:13.361 position:50% align:center
