00:19:15.321 --> 00:19:19.034 position:50% align:center
But as of today, I'm the idol
of freedom for the resistance.

00:19:19.117 --> 00:19:20.535 position:50% align:center
Yuki-rin!

00:19:20.618 --> 00:19:23.038 position:50% align:center
