00:19:28.626 --> 00:19:30.128 position:50% align:center
[MUNAKATA]
Can that thing really fight?

00:19:30.211 --> 00:19:32.088 position:50% align:center
[MIMI]
I wish I knew.

00:19:32.172 --> 00:19:34.507 position:50% align:center
