00:19:48.396 --> 00:19:51.274 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:19:51.358 --> 00:19:53.818 position:50% align:center
[MUSASHI]
Say bye-bye, bunny!

00:19:58.156 --> 00:19:59.783 position:50% align:center
I wanted to play
with the shark model,

00:19:59.866 --> 00:20:03.536 position:50% align:center
