00:20:17.550 --> 00:20:19.010 position:50% align:center
[YUKI gasps]

00:20:22.013 --> 00:20:24.099 position:50% align:center
They're all gone.

00:20:27.852 --> 00:20:29.145 position:50% align:center
[YUKI]
I'm an idol,

00:20:29.229 --> 00:20:31.690 position:50% align:center
and everyone's
supposed to love idols.

00:20:31.773 --> 00:20:34.275 position:50% align:center
That's what it means
to be one. Right?

00:20:34.359 --> 00:20:35.985 position:50% align:center
Yuki.

00:20:36.069 --> 00:20:38.154 position:50% align:center
