a real idol would do

00:20:38.238 --> 00:20:40.949 position:50% align:center
if they were you.

00:20:41.032 --> 00:20:44.953 position:50% align:center
It's no use,
I'm coming up blank.

00:20:46.037 --> 00:20:48.915 position:50% align:center
[YUKI screams]

00:20:50.750 --> 00:20:52.252 position:50% align:center
[MUSASHI]
What a pathetic opponent.

00:20:52.335 --> 00:20:54.421 position:50% align:center
I did want something to crush,

00:20:54.504 --> 00:20:55.922 position:50% align:center
but I thought it'd
be more worthwhile

00:20:56.006 --> 00:20:57.590 position:50% align:center
than a metallic slug with ears!

00:20:57.674 --> 00:20:59.509 position:50% align:center
Yuki!

00:21:02.762 --> 00:21:05.140 position:50% align:center
I'll lay waste to you right
along with this trash heap

00:21:05.223 --> 00:21:08.601 position:50% align:center
you have the gall
to call a city!

00:21:08.685 --> 00:21:10.395 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:21:10.478 --> 00:21:13.398 position:50% align:center
[YAKUMO] And that's the sound
of the left arm overheating.

00:21:13.481 --> 00:21:16.860 position:50% align:center
It appears you've used more
power than it has to give.

00:21:16.943 --> 00:21:19.779 position:50% align:center
It's difficult to handle,
yet delicate as a flower.

00:21:19.863 --> 00:21:21.281 position:50% align:center
[AKATSUKI]
Enough of your sass.

00:21:21.364 --> 00:21:24.826 position:50% align:center
