assault and return to base.

00:21:25.827 --> 00:21:30.623 position:50% align:center
Roger that. Consider this
test run officially complete.

00:21:30.707 --> 00:21:32.042 position:50% align:center
[AKATSUKI]
Good.

00:21:34.711 --> 00:21:39.466 position:50% align:center
Akihabara. This won't be
the last you see of me.

00:21:55.940 --> 00:21:58.526 position:50% align:center
[HOSOMICHI]
Yuki, I...

00:22:04.032 --> 00:22:09.329 position:50% align:center
The Garann's broken.
Just like my dream.

